{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But a few weeks later, the whole of the ghetto has to march out to an appel out in the valley between Bohusovice and Theresienstadt, which in Czech is called Bohusovicka kotlina. 'Kotlina' means valley.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's actually a very flat valley.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The crematorium was in the Bohusovicka kotlina.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By the way, 'crematorium,' you mustn't run away with the idea of gassing or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just people who died of natural causes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Lots of people died in Theresienstadt of natural causes, because of the privations-- cold and, you know, old people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you got ill, you died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Children died of various contagious diseases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But-- so these bodies were disposed of in the-- in this crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, we were all going out to this county.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was once.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once only, because we were never counted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I could-- we were standing, all the young people together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans counted us once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They counted us a second time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stood a whole day and into the night. 100,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's quite a-- can you-- can you think of 100,000 people being counted, standing in so many-- you know, everyone stood with the people that he lived with, but in rows of five, counting.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for some reason, the German couldn't-- the Germans couldn't come to the number that they required.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And between one counting and the other counting, there would be some sort of reckoning that went on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It would be a few hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Leo comes, you know, red bands, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] two-- two first aiders with a stretcher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he says to me, quick, duck under.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the stretcher bearers are taking me into the city, through the gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
